Package: clinAnnotR
Title: Publication-Quality Clinical Time-Series Figures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Given", "Family", , "given.family@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates multi-panel figures combining arbitrary numerical
    laboratory time-series with per-case treatment Gantt charts. Any parameter
    can be displayed as a line or point series on log10 or linear scales, with
    below-detection-limit handling and optional direct value labels. Every
    visual element—colours, shapes, axis ranges, BDL floor, and layout—is
    configurable through function arguments.
